### Create a user [POST]
+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "email_address":"dsafanyuk@shmoople.com",
            "password":"notpassword",
            "room_num":"6326",
            "is_courier":"0",
            "credit_card_number":"12345678980",
            "ccv":"123",
            "exp_date":"0123",
            "wallet":"1.23",
            "first_name":"dave",
            "last_name":"safanyuk"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /user/{user_id}

    + Body

            {
                "user_id": "1",
                "created_at": "2015-08-05T08:40:51.620Z",
                "username": "dsafanyuk",
                "money added": "5.00"
            }

